OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fhas said that some of the cases linked
OL,8,Fto the recent Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,9,Fare caused by a strain known as
OL,10,Fmeningitis B, or MenB.
OL,12,FTwo students from Kent have died of
OL,13,Fthe disease, while several more are in
OL,14,Fserious condition in hospital.
OL,16,FUKHSA, which is investigating the
OL,17,Foutbreak, said it would confirm the
OL,18,Fstrain seen in other cases "when we
OL,19,Fhave the full results".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
