OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FMeningococcus can live harmlessly in
OL,7,Fpeople's throats but can cause serious
OL,8,Fillness if it gets into the blood or
OL,9,Fspinal fluid.
OL,11,FAccording to Meningitis Now, around
OL,12,F10% of the population carries
OL,13,Fmeningococcal bacteria in the back of
OL,14,Ftheir throats at any given time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
