CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FWhy are young people at risk?
OL,8,FAccording to Meningitis Now, one in
OL,9,Ffour 15 to 19-year-olds carry
OL,10,Fmeningococcal bacteria in the back of
OL,11,Ftheir throats, compared with one in 10
OL,12,Fof the UK population.
OL,14,FPeople can carry this harmlessly
OL,15,Fwithout becoming unwell, but it can be
OL,16,Fpassed from person to person by
OL,17,Fcoughing, sneezing, and kissing.
OL,19,FIncreased social interaction in this
OL,20,Fage group means the bacteria can be
OL,21,Fpassed on more easily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FIn universities, students can be more
OL,7,Fvulnerable because of living in more
OL,8,F"cramped" housing or halls of
OL,9,Fresidence.
OL,11,FYoung people also come together from
OL,12,Fall over the world to live, study, and
OL,13,Fsocialise.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FSo can young people get the MenB jab?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FMeningitis Now has called for
OL,7,Fteenagers and young people to be
OL,8,Fvaccinated against meningitis B on the
OL,9,FNHS.
OL,11,FIt launched a new campaign ` No Plan B
OL,12,Ffor MenB ` calling for MenB jabs to be
OL,13,Fgiven to those most at risk, plus a
OL,14,Fbooster programme to protect
OL,15,Fadolescents from 2030.
OL,17,FThe charity also says MenB jabs should
OL,18,Fbe available on the high street "at a
OL,19,Ffair price".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FThe jab is available privately,
OL,7,Fcosting around #110 per dose, with a
OL,8,Fminimum of two doses required.
OL,10,FWhat are the symptoms of meningitis?
OL,12,FSymptoms of meningitis and sepsis can
OL,13,Finclude a high temperature, cold hands
OL,14,Fand feet, vomiting, confusion, muscle
OL,15,Fand joint pain, pale, mottled or
OL,16,Fblotchy skin, spots or a rash, a
OL,17,Fheadache, a stiff neck, aversion to
OL,18,Fbright lights, being very sleepy, and
OL,19,Fseizures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773774689
OL,3,CWhat do we know about Meningitis B and
OL,4,Chow serious is it?
OL,6,FSymptoms can appear in any order, and
OL,7,Fsome may not appear at all.
OL,9,FThe UK Health Security Agency advises
OL,10,Fcalling 999 immediately or going to
OL,11,Fyour nearest A&E if you think you or
OL,12,Fsomeone in your care could have
OL,13,Fmeningitis or septicaemia, as people
OL,14,Fcan become unwell very quickly.
OL,16,FYou can call NHS 111 if you're unsure
OL,17,Fwhether it's serious.
OL,19,FHow is meningitis treated?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
